title: People Holding Hands Medium Dark Skin Tone Medium Skin Tone
description: Represents two people, with medium-dark and medium skin tones respectively, holding hands. This emoji conveys a sense of connection, partnership, love, or friendship between individuals with similar, yet distinct, complexions.
apple_vendor_description: Apple's rendition of people holding hands with medium-dark and medium skin tones is a vibrant symbol of connection and unity, rendered with Apple's characteristic smooth gradients and rounded edges. The hands are shown clasped firmly, with subtle shading that emphasizes their closeness and warmth, reflecting Apple's inclusive design philosophy. This emoji powerfully communicates friendship, romance, and solidarity in digital communication.
